rows.label: tlk70000001_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Seeing everyone hard at work
remind Morumo of old story.

rows.label: tlk70000001_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Was not easy to gain trust
of people. Morumo ran self
ragged every day.

rows.label: tlk70000001_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Made many mistakes. Caused people
lot of trouble. But good learning
experience. Gave Morumo realization.

rows.label: tlk70000001_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Realized that failure or
success not end. Keeping
going what really matter.

rows.label: tlk70000001_03_msg0005
rows.name:
That why Morumo think
everyone need variety!

rows.label: tlk70000001_03_msg0006
rows.name:
Alst big place, and only one chance
at life. Shame to waste it!
